615
00:31:05,720 --> 00:31:06,470
today.

616
00:31:07,160 --> 00:31:08,240
I don't want to hear it anymore.

617
00:31:08,240 --> 00:31:08,830
Suoluo.

618
00:31:12,280 --> 00:31:13,410
I've heard about it.

619
00:31:15,310 --> 00:31:16,470
If you are doing this

620
00:31:16,640 --> 00:31:18,030
just to spite me,

621
00:31:18,670 --> 00:31:19,600
there is no need.

622
00:31:20,670 --> 00:31:21,930
I hope you understand.

623
00:31:23,010 --> 00:31:24,040
Don't do anything

624
00:31:24,070 --> 00:31:25,470
you'd regret.

625
00:31:26,070 --> 00:31:27,400
I never regret what I do.

626
00:31:27,790 --> 00:31:29,720
Neither do I need anyone's advice.

627
00:31:30,720 --> 00:31:31,470
If there's

628
00:31:31,490 --> 00:31:32,290
nothing else,

629
00:31:33,110 --> 00:31:34,170
I'll take my leave.

630
00:31:34,920 --> 00:31:35,590
Suoluo!

631
00:31:48,510 --> 00:31:49,240
How did it go?

632
00:31:49,270 --> 00:31:50,880
How was your talk with Suoluo?

633
00:31:50,880 --> 00:31:52,110
She has her own matters to worry about.

634
00:31:52,110 --> 00:31:53,640
Let's think of another way.

635
00:31:56,910 --> 00:31:58,440
You told me to wait for you.

636
00:31:59,350 --> 00:32:01,010
What were you going to tell me?

637
00:32:04,390 --> 00:32:05,790
The moon is full tonight.

638
00:32:07,710 --> 00:32:08,990
Yes, what about it?

639
00:32:13,310 --> 00:32:14,310
Come home with me.

640
00:32:15,050 --> 00:32:16,310
We'll sleep together.

641
00:32:20,810 --> 00:32:21,870
Have you forgotten

642
00:32:22,190 --> 00:32:23,150
our promise?

643
00:32:24,030 --> 00:32:25,560
I'll watch you shapeshift.

644
00:32:36,140 --> 00:32:37,230
You once said

645
00:32:38,730 --> 00:32:39,390
you didn't know

646
00:32:39,390 --> 00:32:41,190
what you would shapeshift into.

647
00:32:41,890 --> 00:32:42,750
You didn't know

648
00:32:43,430 --> 00:32:45,630
what kind of danger you would be facing.

649
00:32:46,270 --> 00:32:47,330
I want to be with you

650
00:32:48,750 --> 00:32:50,210
so that you won't be lonely

651
00:32:50,910 --> 00:32:51,970
or afraid anymore.

652
00:33:05,230 --> 00:33:05,990
Well?

653
00:33:07,190 --> 00:33:08,650
Are you going back with me?

654
00:33:32,100 --> 00:33:33,460
This is what you meant

655
00:33:34,590 --> 00:33:35,850
by sleeping together?

656
00:33:37,710 --> 00:33:38,390
What else?

657
00:33:43,710 --> 00:33:44,170
Then...

658
00:33:44,990 --> 00:33:47,250
You're just gonna sit there and watch me?

659
00:33:48,270 --> 00:33:48,750
Yes.

660
00:33:52,510 --> 00:33:53,170
Go to sleep.

661
00:33:56,500 --> 00:33:57,760
Are you really going to

662
00:33:57,930 --> 00:33:59,390
sit and watch me all night?

663
00:34:02,890 --> 00:34:04,870
But I don't think it's appropriate.

664
00:34:04,870 --> 00:34:06,530
I can't bear to let you do that.

665
00:34:06,710 --> 00:34:07,760
This is your bed.

666
00:34:07,920 --> 00:34:09,640
But I'm lying here and you're sitting there.

667
00:34:09,640 --> 00:34:10,970
That's inappropriate.

668
00:34:11,310 --> 00:34:12,170
How about this?

669
00:34:12,550 --> 00:34:13,390
We'll each take

670
00:34:13,390 --> 00:34:14,250
half of the bed.

671
00:34:14,410 --> 00:34:15,670
We'll sleep together.

672
00:34:37,989 --> 00:34:38,790
This can't do.

673
00:34:39,870 --> 00:34:41,330
I have to keep an eye on you.

674
00:35:41,390 --> 00:35:41,950
Zhiyi.

675
00:35:43,990 --> 00:35:46,050
You didn't sleep well again, did you?

676
00:35:46,160 --> 00:35:47,490
Have some ginseng soup.

677
00:35:47,910 --> 00:35:48,510
Here.

678
00:35:50,200 --> 00:35:51,390
My two kids

679
00:35:53,350 --> 00:35:55,230
are taking turns to worry me.

680
00:35:59,270 --> 00:36:00,200
How can I be fine?

681
00:36:05,430 --> 00:36:06,070
Honey.

682
00:36:07,390 --> 00:36:08,270
I asked you

683
00:36:08,290 --> 00:36:09,620
to keep an eye on Xinbai.

684
00:36:09,950 --> 00:36:10,470
Is he

685
00:36:10,470 --> 00:36:11,730
up to anything lately?

686
00:36:12,110 --> 00:36:13,510
Don't cry.

687
00:36:15,190 --> 00:36:16,310
Xinbai

688
00:36:17,030 --> 00:36:18,470
has grown up.

689
00:36:20,950 --> 00:36:23,280
Is Yan Nanxing staying at his place again?

690
00:36:24,030 --> 00:36:24,870
Is she?

691
00:37:28,990 --> 00:37:29,850
Yan Nanxing...

692
00:37:33,000 --> 00:37:34,330
You didn't shapeshift.

693
00:37:39,270 --> 00:37:40,150
If not today,

694
00:37:40,340 --> 00:37:41,670
it'll happen tomorrow.

695
00:37:42,210 --> 00:37:44,940
It's either before or after the full moon anyway.

696
00:37:46,540 --> 00:37:47,590
Really?

697
00:37:48,750 --> 00:37:49,230
Yes.

698
00:37:53,310 --> 00:37:54,070
Well...

699
00:37:54,540 --> 00:37:56,270
Since I haven't shapeshifted,

700
00:37:57,310 --> 00:37:59,400
I'm going back to Blossom Beauty first.

701
00:37:59,400 --> 00:38:00,600
I'll be back tonight.

702
00:38:01,470 --> 00:38:02,390
Again?

703
00:38:03,710 --> 00:38:04,070
Yes.

704
00:38:18,110 --> 00:38:19,030
Yan Nanxing!

705
00:38:21,950 --> 00:38:22,750
What's wrong?

706
00:38:23,230 --> 00:38:24,190
Your mother!

707
00:38:24,400 --> 00:38:25,040
My mother?

708
00:38:25,070 --> 00:38:25,670
Hurry up.

709
00:38:25,880 --> 00:38:26,510
Come on.

710
00:38:28,010 --> 00:38:29,350
Why is my mother here?

711
00:38:29,370 --> 00:38:30,300
