712
00:38:31,440 --> 00:38:32,480
Hurry up.

713
00:38:32,510 --> 00:38:33,440
Where do I go?

714
00:38:33,830 --> 00:38:34,230
Hurry.

715
00:38:34,410 --> 00:38:35,340
Coming, Mother!

716
00:38:38,390 --> 00:38:39,590
Close the door for me.

717
00:38:39,710 --> 00:38:40,710
Coming, Mother!

718
00:38:44,600 --> 00:38:45,800
Where is Yan Nanxing?

719
00:38:46,630 --> 00:38:47,190
Where is Yan Nanxing?

720
00:38:47,190 --> 00:38:47,630
She...

721
00:38:47,750 --> 00:38:49,110
I saw her open the door.

722
00:38:49,340 --> 00:38:50,070
Where is she?

723
00:38:50,510 --> 00:38:51,390
No, she...

724
00:38:53,480 --> 00:38:54,350
Calm down.

725
00:38:54,970 --> 00:38:56,670
Were you sleeping together?

726
00:38:59,570 --> 00:39:01,210
I agreed to let you run Blossom Beauty together,

727
00:39:01,210 --> 00:39:03,070
