732
00:39:09,960 --> 00:39:11,290
What do you mean by that?

733
00:39:11,290 --> 00:39:12,350
It's not like that!

734
00:39:18,320 --> 00:39:18,990
Mother.

735
00:39:19,720 --> 00:39:20,310
Mother!

736
00:39:20,460 --> 00:39:21,190
Yan Nanxing!

737
00:39:23,610 --> 00:39:24,210
Mother...

738
00:39:35,270 --> 00:39:36,200
I can explain...

739
00:39:42,790 --> 00:39:43,310
You...

740
00:39:44,440 --> 00:39:46,270
He... He!

741
00:39:48,350 --> 00:39:48,860
You!

742
00:39:49,120 --> 00:39:49,600
You are...

743
00:39:49,600 --> 00:39:50,710
I'm not.

744
00:39:51,270 --> 00:39:51,930
He's not...

745
00:39:52,750 --> 00:39:53,350
I am.

746
00:39:54,510 --> 00:39:55,030
He is...

747
00:39:55,940 --> 00:39:56,630
He's not...

748
00:39:56,950 --> 00:39:57,390
You...

749
00:39:59,150 --> 00:39:59,630
Mother.

750
00:39:59,650 --> 00:40:00,710
It's not like that.

